.DT
query_discussion_item_by_type
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_discussion_item_by_type

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_discussion_item_by_type -  This method figures out the discussion item for the club with the given type.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
class discussion_idea query_discussion_item_by_type(string club_name,
int type,
class discussion_idea idea)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^club_name%^RESET%^ - the name of the club
%^BOLD%^type%^RESET%^ - the type of the discussion item to find
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the found discussion item
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/inherit/club_discuss.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method figures out the discussion item for the club with the
given type.  It will also continue on a search from a last found item.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
add_discussion_item()

.EP

